</div>

<div class="unit one-of-three">
<h2>Cross Platform</h2>
Works on Desktop (Win, Mac, Linux), Android, iOS and HTML5.
</div>

<div class="unit one-of-three">
<h2>Modular</h2>
The modular architecture allows third party modules to be easily added.
</div>

<div class="unit one-of-three">
<h2>super fast</h2>
Heavy emphasis on avoiding garbage collection for Dalvik/JavaScript by careful API design and the use of custom collection.
</div>

<div class="unit one-of-three">
<h2>Community Support</h2>
